Development Changelog
'''''''''''''''''''''

- Introduce FA bridge watchtower. (MR :gl:`!17984`)
- The FA bridge watchtower becomes the bridge watchtower.
  It becomes generic over the type of bridge it monitors.
  From now on the watchtower will monitor events related
  to both the XTZ and FA bridge and will claim deposits
  for both bridges. (MR :gl:`!20558`)
